  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_8_5465-5510",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5465-5510",
      "markText": "晚清中国历史固然充满了挫折和屈辱，但放眼整个非西方世界，它更是一部国家转型非常成功的历史。",
      "totalCount": 600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5465&rangeEnd=5510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5465&rangeEnd=5510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_38_949-1003",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "949-1003",
      "markText": "假如日本的全面侵华战争爆发于国民党统一全国、蒋介石巩固其国家领袖地位之前的话，中华民国的生存机会将会很渺茫。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=949&rangeEnd=1003",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=949&rangeEnd=1003"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_6_7851-7886",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7851-7886",
      "markText": "这里的一个终极问题是，今天的中国是否为一具有历史合法性的“民族国家”？",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7851&rangeEnd=7886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7851&rangeEnd=7886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_4_905-967",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "905-967",
      "markText": "这些问题不解释清楚，中国作为一个现代国家的历史正当性，及其在西方历史经验基础上所建构的国际政治话语中的合法性，便会受到质疑。",
      "totalCount": 350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=905&rangeEnd=967",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=905&rangeEnd=967"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_6_5799-5877",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5799-5877",
      "markText": "不过1949年之前和之后流行于中国的民族主义历史书写只突出晚清以来的“百年屈辱”，远不足以全面概括中国在这一个世纪所经历的突破和坎坷（H.Li 2013）。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5799&rangeEnd=5877",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5799&rangeEnd=5877"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_7_2453-2505",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2453-2505",
      "markText": "一个国家是否能够克服内外挑战，很大程度上取决于其财政和军事实力，进而言之，乃取决于国家对经济的抽取能力。",
      "totalCount": 299,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2453&rangeEnd=2505",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2453&rangeEnd=2505"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_25_8575-8664",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "8575-8664",
      "markText": "清政府之所以在海防上如此吝啬，并非完全因为它缺乏财力，而是因为它缺乏加大北洋水师和其他舰队投入力度的决心，而这又可进一步归咎于清廷对地缘政治形势的认知，这才是甲午战败的最根本原因",
      "totalCount": 285,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=8575&rangeEnd=8664",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=8575&rangeEnd=8664"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_6_7481-7522",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7481-7522",
      "markText": "质言之，中国和其他非西方国家的区别之处，在于其兼具幅员辽阔的国土和强大的行政力量。",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7481&rangeEnd=7522",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7481&rangeEnd=7522"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_3_1165-1245",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1165-1245",
      "markText": "我们的“实践社会科学系列”倡导把上述的认知过程颠倒过来，不是从源自西方的理论及由此得出的理论假说出发，而是从研究对象国家的实践历史与现实出发，而后进入理论建构。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1165&rangeEnd=1245",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1165&rangeEnd=1245"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_11_3623-3709",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3623-3709",
      "markText": "与此同时，由于喇嘛教虔诚信众脱离生产，不结婚生育，满人统治精英还把喇嘛教视作控制蒙古人势力壮大的有效手段；事实上也是如此，在整个清代，无论外蒙古还是内蒙古，人口都一直在下降",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3623&rangeEnd=3709",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3623&rangeEnd=3709"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_6_6225-6264",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6225-6264",
      "markText": "因此，这里需要探究，为什么数个世纪以来的国家转型过程会反复出现此一阶段性结局。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6225&rangeEnd=6264",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6225&rangeEnd=6264"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_43_2058-2148",
      "chapterUid": 43,
      "range": "2058-2148",
      "markText": "正是财政软肋以及因此带来的军事颓势，而不是其他因素，构成红军在1934年10月第五次反“围剿”失败的主要原因；此次“围剿”，国民政府共动用了100万名士兵、200架飞机及各种火炮。",
      "totalCount": 266,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=43&rangeStart=2058&rangeEnd=2148",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=43&rangeStart=2058&rangeEnd=2148"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_7_1771-1817",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1771-1817",
      "markText": "东亚的朝贡体系只是礼仪性的，只是朝廷确认其统治地位以及属国换取认可和保护的一种互利性需求而已",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1771&rangeEnd=1817",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1771&rangeEnd=1817"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_4_1220-1297",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1220-1297",
      "markText": "在革命和现代化宏大叙事失去了往日魅力之后，人们纷纷埋头从事过去一直被边缘化的课题的研究，诸如妇女、性别、宗族、民间宗教、地方社会及各种边缘群体和边缘现象。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1220&rangeEnd=1297",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1220&rangeEnd=1297"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_4_598-631",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "598-631",
      "markText": "一个现代国家的形成，离不开四个基本要素，即领土、人口、政府和主权。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=598&rangeEnd=631",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=598&rangeEnd=631"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_8_3252-3316",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3252-3316",
      "markText": "清朝治理边疆的目标，并不是要那里提供贡赋或税款，以增加自身的税收，而是要确保边疆的稳定，使之对其核心地带和核心利益起到保障作用。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3252&rangeEnd=3316",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3252&rangeEnd=3316"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_10_6435-6512",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "6435-6512",
      "markText": "对于清朝来说，边陲诸部落是其战略安全或地缘利益之命脉所系，但对其财政收入或经济利益方面并不重要；而对于欧洲各强国而言，建立殖民地的主要目的是获得经济回报。",
      "totalCount": 230,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6435&rangeEnd=6512",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6435&rangeEnd=6512"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_8_4424-4477",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4424-4477",
      "markText": "清朝之所以可以称之为“中国”的一个朝代，而非满人的或是亚洲内陆的帝国，正因为它一直以内地各省为国祚之根本。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4424&rangeEnd=4477",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4424&rangeEnd=4477"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_8_10115-10183",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10115-10183",
      "markText": "1937年后，日本的全面侵华战争进一步中断了国民党的国家统一和重建事业，与此同时，中共在抗战后方不断发展壮大，最终成为国民党最大的对手。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300025080&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10115&rangeEnd=10183",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6ec32c50813ab704cg010728?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10115&rangeEnd=10183"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300025080_35_1416-1504",
